<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼妈妈非常惊讶，目不转睛地盯着那个小人类。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真小！”狼妈妈温柔地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个小男孩儿挤进两只狼宝宝中间取暖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你看！他不怕我们，也不怕宝宝们。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我听说过有人类小孩儿和狼群一起生活。”狼爸爸说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可是，在我们狼群里，我从来没见过。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48614</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，狼爸爸和狼妈妈听到什么声音，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48614</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>朝洞口转过身去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55618</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>原来是塔巴其和老虎谢尔坎来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55618</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57954</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个小孩儿在这儿，主人！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57954</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>豺狼兴奋地喊着，“我看见他了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68818</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢尔坎，您的来访让我们非常荣幸。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼爸爸很有礼貌地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但他的双眼却闪烁着愤怒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您需要什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83404</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一个人类孩子朝这边儿走了。”谢尔坎说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83404</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他的父母逃跑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>把人类的孩子交给我。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95155</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>幸好洞口很窄，谢尔坎进不来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95155</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们狼是自由的动物。”狼爸爸说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103315</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们听头狼的话，不听你的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103315</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109353</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老虎的怒吼在洞里回荡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109353</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼妈妈跳到了谢尔坎面前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在黑暗中，她的眼睛像两个绿色的月亮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124105</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个人类孩子是我的！”狼妈妈咆哮着，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124105</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“孩子不会被杀死的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130760</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子会和狼群一起奔跑，和狼群一起打猎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130760</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134486</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，请你离开，谢尔坎！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134486</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼爸爸惊讶地看着这一幕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼爸爸忘了他的妻子生气时会有多可怕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146404</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>谢尔坎退到洞口外面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我等着看狼群会怎么处理人类的孩子！”他龇牙低吼，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个孩子是我的，他会死在我的牙下！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼妈妈跳到宝宝们中间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173401</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼爸爸看着老虎大步离开。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173401</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢尔坎说了一个事实。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼爸爸说着叹了一口气，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们必须给狼群看这个人类孩子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你真的打算收留他吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192178</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我当然要收留他！”狼妈妈厉声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192178</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196907</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个可怜的小家伙晚上自己饿着肚子来到这里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196907</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我要给他起名叫毛克利。”她接着说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204270</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“总有一天，他会抓到谢尔坎，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204270</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207769</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就像那只老虎抓他一样。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207769</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼爸爸很担心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212154</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们狼群会说什么呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212154</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>森林法则很清楚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224704</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼群保护小狼直到他们足够强大去自己打猎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224704</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230703</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，狼群好像不会保护一个人类宝宝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230703</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233101</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们以后再说这件事吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233101</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼妈妈坚定地回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个月月圆的时候，狼群就开一次会。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246967</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有的新父母都要给大家看他们的孩子们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246967</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250473</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在下一次狼群会议的那天晚上，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250473</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254922</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼爸爸和狼妈妈去参加岩石会议。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261019</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼宝宝们和毛克利跟在他们后面跑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261019</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>岩石会议在山顶上开，那里有很多石头和巨石。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿克拉是最厉害的大灰狼，他趴在一块岩石上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278775</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，他领导这个狼群已经一年了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278775</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282297</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他是一只智慧、健壮的头狼，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282297</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285376</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>了解人类的方式和习俗。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>岩石会议非常安静。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291769</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有的父母都围成了一个圆圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297212</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在圆圈中央，狼宝宝们一起打滚、玩耍。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297212</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303461</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼父母们一个接一个地给大家看自己的孩子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>303268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，大家快看！”阿克拉喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315519</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼妈妈们激动地重复道：“哦，大家快看！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>315519</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼妈妈的毛抖了一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>323768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>差不多到时候该给大家看毛克利了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>323768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>333563</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼群看到这个长相奇怪的人类宝宝会说什么呢？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>